        'decision_prompt'      => 'How will you manage the developing cargo shift and its safety implications? Address: your immediate actions to assess and correct the vessel\'s stability, the plan for re-securing the cargo considering crew safety in heavy weather, your routing decision (continue to Antalya, divert to Marmaris, or other options), ISM incident reporting to the DPA, and how you will prepare for the likely PSC inspection at your next port.',
